{"tid":289881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★27歲IT男陳屍家中","createTime":"2017-06-19T10:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T06:13:15.000Z","uid":19454,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3573fe1f14edd2e4ffcf288f92671029ac6b717a","tid":289881,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:57:53.000Z","msg":"一名男子多日沒有上班，及後被發現身穿日式女子水手裝、黑色絲襪，陳屍住所中。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地一住宅大樓5樓單位，這名身材瘦削的男子在網絡公司工作，因其母親一直未能聯絡上他，便讓親戚上門查看，未料來到單位門口時，卻發現大門反鎖，破門入屋後，驚見男子身穿水手裝、黑絲襪，臉部朝下趴在室內，遂即報警。<br />\n警方與救護員趕到現場後，證實他已經死亡，但初步調查已排除他殺，正朝家居意外死亡方向調查。<br />\n附近鄰居稱，這男子姓孫，27歲，獨居於這個單位，為人不錯，但較內向，不太與其他人說話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170619/56843559\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170619%2F56843559&d=O23klGfIocB0W2ueYgB4hv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=e55a775c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170619%2F56843559&h=1f09ecb7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170619/56843559</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170618/large/1497800424_987e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170618%2Flarge%2F1497800424_987e.jpg&h=abec551a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50fb6f1182a0332ab3f1234f868809ba61305ed8","tid":289881,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:58:39.000Z","msg":"打J死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dae2c75efbe571067776310f88a4628d8d6e859b","tid":289881,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:59:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">男子在網絡公司工作<br />\n男子在網絡公司工作<br />\n男子在網絡公司工作<br />\n男子在網絡公司工作<br />\n男子在網絡公司工作</span>"},{"pid":"58095bc03ee0c58f81ecaa2b9c4e6311923b7ca5","tid":289881,"uid"